库存在单独的 block 竞争，下面来看这个 latch 存在的子 latch 及其对应的类型：
SQL> SELECT addr, latch#, gets, misses, sleeps
     FROM v$latch_children
     WHERE sleeps>0
     and latch# = 98
     ORDER BY sleeps desc;



